{"tid":155021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩國爆「大戰」 中國冰球員失控狂毆南韓球員","createTime":"2017-03-13T17:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T00:43:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2dfcd0fe7978da84261e914dd1a8a7878d5a6a08","tid":155021,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170313/large/1489408118_7fda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170313%2Flarge%2F1489408118_7fda.jpg&h=26f97609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170313/56423343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170313%2F56423343&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2877d7fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170313%2F56423343&h=b20ee440\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170313/56423343</a><br />\n美韓落實部署「薩德」防禦系統，讓中韓關係緊張。雙方竟在冰球場上率先爆發中韓大戰。<br />\n<br />\n前日，亞洲冰球聯賽常規賽，中國冰鶴龍之隊主隊迎戰南韓大明隊，當兩隊比數3比3時，雙方球員激烈衝撞後爆發衝突。其中，22歲的中國球員張鋮將南韓球員按在地上暴打，隨後雙方展開大規模身體衝突，比賽一度長時間中斷。<br />\n有指，衝突源於南韓隊員在中場附近撞倒張鋮撞翻在地，張鋮起身後試圖找對方理論，但對方不斷推搡。據現場影片所見，張鋮失控按着南韓球員狂毆，扭打在一團。有南韓球員曾企圖上前分開二人，惟卻遭中國球員阻止。<br />\n2014年，亞洲冰球聯賽中，中韓兩隊也曾在賽場爆發群毆大戰，導火線也正是今次涉事「主角」張鋮。當時在一次中場爭搶中，張鋮被南韓隊球員衝撞，隨後他追上該球員與其「單挑」。"},{"pid":"0fe9081d24cb9af5099c2e0a72e4b6e8363c54d6","tid":155021,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"支那黃種馬騮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5162c91d97a1137fc30b8363b40158295d98deea","tid":155021,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T23:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3add51e596634e2498abfe8330930679e75dad03","tid":155021,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T23:02:05.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239fe3df630d5c09df49bb86bd06980dfe987f7c","tid":155021,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T23:02:26.000Z","msg":"本是同根生"},{"pid":"04ec9e0fa5d82d4c147287e47a70cf2b87380679","tid":155021,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:25:57.000Z","msg":"大家也是泡菜狗，不要分得那麼細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b290a43ae386420a9c9d19c51bae5f0db3fbb2","tid":155021,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113e69ebf25ef09d1dd24869db0f9e5f68176c78","tid":155021,"uid":5149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"呢排睇住兩個最憎既垃圾國家狗咬狗真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}